creator: ZSS Tecnologia
descriptionHtml:
The Hortify app is specialized in horticulture and floriculture and aims to help rural producers and partners to manage their business, always valuing the quality of production and the impact on the quality of life of the planet and the people who consume it.

You will find features that will help you accomplish:
- Labor management of your property
- Production management, field notebook and food traceability
- Financial management
- Inventory management
- Central purchasing system

Do as more than 1,000 producers and install the app now.

On the website www.hortify.app you will find all the benefits of the application, remembering that the application is free, but to access some features you must purchase one of our plans as needed. Consult our commercial sector (19) 98324-0110
descriptionShort: We help horticulturalists to manage their business

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Several improvements and integration between crop management and financial management, enabling the control of accounts receivable related to crop sales;
- Improvements in crop control with the consolidation of the number of sales per lot;
- New visualization of activities in progress in the labor-management module;
- Visualization of labor expenses by production;
